Misc Utilities¶

Misc utilities.

gensaschema._util.cmp(a, b)¶
gensaschema._util.find_public(space)[source]¶

Determine all public names in space

If the space contains an __all__ sequence, a copy is returned (as a list). Otherwise, all symbol names not starting with an underscore are listed.

Parameters:

space (dict) – Name space to inspect

Returns:

List of public names

Return type:

list
